#BMI-Calculator

Hi, this is a small project which use to calculate the Body Mass Index(BMI). 
The formula to calculate BMI is weight/height*height
I using Python to make it and below is its result:
Welcome to the BMI Calculator!
Enter your weight in kg: (exp 63)
Enter your height in m: (exp 1.60)
Your BMI is: 24.61
You are normal weight.

#Preview
(You can do it in Python to calculate the BMI)

##How to Run
1. Install Python(recommend version 3.13)
2. Run the code

##Key Technologies
-Python core programming language
-Pycharm IDE used for development
-Command Line Interface(CLI) User interaction method

